caption.text: Magic of christmas not only fills in your heart, but it spreads to your loved ones. Merry christmas to you and your family!

The prevalence of hypertension in Jatinangor has reached 37.98%. It's more than the national prevalence itself, 26%
.
I, Gerald Ethelie, support CORONER, Community of Hypertension Eradicators. A sustainable project by CIMSA FK Unpad that is intended to help decreasing the number of complication caused by hypertension in Jatinangor by educating cadre specifically in Desa Cipacing RW 2 & RW 8. As hypertension is one of main risk factors for stroke, dementia, and heart coronary disease, it is important not to underestimate its occurence
.
"Making changes isn't easy. It requires consistent effort & persistant spirit."
.
So let's be part of the change and support CORONER!
